<TEXTAREA NAME="Text" COLS="60" ROWS="6" WRAP="VIRTUAL" >Well i know everyone wants a knuckles chao and u can only get it at a japanese convention which happened many years ago but i NEARLY got a knuckles chao by myself and here is how i done it.....

Well 1st of all you will need a chao obviously if u want him to go up quick get a chao that as a C,B or A rank Power. Then give it the Red Chaos drives until it evolves into a Neutral/Power chao.
this is the most IMPORTANT bit of them all. Give it only PURPLE chaos drives nothing else. If u do it will totally wreck the whole knuckles chao system. If u keep on feeding it purple chaos drives u will see the difference just keep on looking at the chao's hands u will see little pointy bits that u would see with knuckles. After that i don't know what to do really i hope anyone has good ideas how to do it i done it that way but it wen't back into a neutral chao and it was supposed to go onto a knuckles chao when it came out of the egg :(

Well good luck people and maybe u will get that exclusive knuckles chao everyone is wanting to get their hands on ^-^

</TEXTAREA></TD>

